'''''''''''''''

************** Steps to run the PLS End-to-End Tests ************ 	

1. Setup properties(write the properties in config.ini file). Two options to achieve this:
	Option 1:
		1) cd to ../le-tools/PLSEnd2End/
		2) run the script setUpProperties.py with the properties
	Option 2: change the config.ini file manually
 
2. Setup PLS, including drop templates, configure DL/VDB and set up Load Groups. To do this:
	1) cd to ../le-tools/PLSEnd2End/
	2) python setUpPLS.py

3. Run Tests:
	1) cd to ../le-tools/PLSEnd2End/
	2) python -m unittest tests.{testModuleName}


'''''''''''''''